snippet.title: Blue Fish and Underwater Worlds - Trailer
snippet.description:
"Blue Fish and Underwater Worlds" video game trailer. 
Blue depths hide many dangers and the food chain knows no mercy. Help Blue Fish eat and not get eaten. Game is available here https://suzanatrifkovic.itch.io/blue-fish-and-underwater-worlds
Engaging 10 levels and relaxing music. The more Blue Fish grows, avoiding predators gets more difficult. Crabs, squids, sharks, jellyfishes, fishing hooks, pearls and mini underwater castles. ​Are you ready to test your swimming skills?
